+| `tests/test_ffi_safety.py`        | `tests/ffi-safety.test.ts`             | ✅ |
+| `tests/test_no_recovery_surface.py` | `tests/no-recovery-surface.test.ts`  | ✅ |
+| `tests/test_save_time_validation.py` | `tests/save-time-validation.test.ts` | ✅ |
