dev/plans/runs/F0-review-20260504T121732Z.md:584:The broader CI gate is `./scripts/check.sh` (adds mkdocs build); the agent-loop gate is `agent-verify.sh`. Long-run test variants (e.g. AC-021 60 s window, AC-059b ~1000-iteration cursor-race fixture) are exercised only via `scripts/check.sh` with `AGENT_LONG=1`; `agent-verify.sh` skips them for runtime budget.
