TE_THREADSAFE=2`/`SQLITE_NO_MUTEX`rebuild) — directly disables per-conn mutex; smaller-radius test.\n- **D.1** (architectural — per-conn lookaside or alt reader topology) — kill mutex track if C.1 also flat.\n\n### next_phase_recommendation: **C1**\n\n### Tests passing pre-revert\nmultithread_wiring (2/2), AC-017 green, AC-018 green, lifecycle_reliability (4/4), vector_contracts (7/7), projection_runtime (12/12), op_store (7/7), error_taxonomy (12/12), instrumentation_methods (5/5), cursor_read_after_write (1/1), search_result_shape (2/2), property_template (1/1), lib (1/1). Pre-existing A.0 compile errors in tests/{compatibility,cursors,lifecycle_observability}.rs unchanged.\n\n### git_status_clean_after_revert: true\n(Only untracked`dev/plans/runs/B1-multithread-wiring-output.json`; production source identical to baseline `fc3dda3`.)"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":656,"cache_read_input_tokens":85490,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":656},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e8e03970-0bb0-4f28-945f-ef09a4c5917b","uuid":"cd90015e-c752-41bd-afde-3ad12c6668f0"}
